Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.27,0:01:34.00,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Is your sister okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.30,0:01:36.27,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.08,0:01:39.11,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.00,0:01:42.58,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.21,0:01:44.08,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.46,0:01:47.00,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I didn’t come because I owe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.45,0:01:51.72,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I want my powers back so \NI can protect everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:54.21,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,That’s all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:01:59.18,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,You won’t admit it, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.48,0:02:06.18,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,This is…my…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:09.89,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,That’s the symbol of your power, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.89,0:02:11.15,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it secure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:14.45,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
