Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:37.69,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu, go to bed already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:39.29,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Karin?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.29,0:02:42.84,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,I... uh…have things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.84,0:02:44.30,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.71,0:02:46.40,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn’t matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:48.00,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,If this is about Brother Ichi,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:50.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll stay up and chew him \Nout when he comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:52.32,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,I’m telling you to go \Nto bed because you have
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.32,0:02:54.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,to cook and stuff in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:57.07,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,Brother’s got nothing to do with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:02:59.74,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not worried about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:02.54,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,It’s okay to be worried, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:04.57,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Ichi’s been \Nacting strangely lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.57,0:03:06.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and it’s only natural to worry when
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:09.02,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,he comes home very late \Nseveral nights in a row!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.02,0:03:10.86,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,I said I’m not worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.86,0:03:11.96,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,You are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:12.92,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not! Get off my case!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:15.53,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:19.55,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I’m home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:22.02,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,-Brother!\N-Brother Ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:25.97,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What? You’re both still up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:27.80,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Go to bed already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:29.30,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You’ll be late for school tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.80,0:03:32.81,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:35.62,B2,YUZU/KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:38.91,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,-Good night, Brother!\N-Good night, Brother Ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:57.45,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,For the past week, I did \Neverything you told me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:03:58.99,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.99,0:04:01.72,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I back here again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.07,0:04:04.80,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,You complain, and yet you came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.54,0:04:06.76,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:07.95,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.25,0:04:12.23,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,You want your Soul Reaper \Npowers back, don’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:14.13,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why I’m here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:19.19,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we’d be doing some \Ntraining-type thing in a big place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:21.63,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:25.10,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,We are doing some training-type \Nthing in a big place!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:29.75,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you staring at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:32.20,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.51,0:04:33.79,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Riruka…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:37.29,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,I think it’s time you \Nstop kicking the door open.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.82,0:04:41.96,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t appreciate having to \Nsee your panties every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.48,0:04:43.92,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:45.33,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Yukio…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.33,0:04:49.89,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you think you \Ncan speak to me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.41,0:04:53.36,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can say whatever you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.36,0:04:56.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,just because we have a guest?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:04:58.28,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, guess again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.28,0:05:01.73,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,A creepy geek like you who plays video games
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:05.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,all day has no right to \Ntalk to me like an equal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:07.11,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:11.37,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve never, then or now, \Nthought of you and me as equals!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:14.76,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.76,0:05:16.73,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,Could you repeat that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.84,0:05:22.75,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah? Yukio… What \Nmakes you think you can…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:25.02,B2,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t have to repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:27.69,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me, Jackie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.69,0:05:28.89,B2,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,All right, all right…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:32.39,B2,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about that and get on with \Nexplaining that box to Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:34.44,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Stop nagging me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:37.09,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t have to remind me. \NI’ll explain it right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:39.39,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you just standing there for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.39,0:05:41.91,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Come over here so I can explain it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:43.50,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, already…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:45.40,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,And why am I being yelled at?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:48.32,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:50.20,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:51.61,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,You’re fine right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.61,0:05:54.46,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t come a step closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:56.76,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,C’mon, make up your mind…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:05.19,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Observe this box!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.19,0:06:06.38,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I’m looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:07.32,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:08.47,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Well what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:10.67,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t it cute?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.67,0:06:11.32,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:13.91,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,You should be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:17.14,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,This cute dollhouse is \Nyour training facility!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:22.41,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:24.54,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t have to understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,0:06:26.61,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll show you soon enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:27.77,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Show me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.77,0:06:29.71,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,My Fullbring!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:33.37,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,My Fullbring is called “Dollhouse”!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:37.71,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,I have the ability to move \Npeople or things at will
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:41.21,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,into and out of objects that I \Nthink are cute or that I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:51.87,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,That’s your pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:54.31,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you can go inside now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:56.64,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Go inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:59.18,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,I permit you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.29,0:07:02.45,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you talking…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.06,0:07:16.92,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt…damn it…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:18.30,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:29.63,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You’re kidding me…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:34.93,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Isn’t it cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:36.80,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Cute, my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:38.56,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:39.71,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Defeat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.71,0:07:40.52,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:41.75,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,You’re so dense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:43.70,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Fight and defeat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:45.63,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,That’s your training!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:47.30,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,You’ll do fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:49.11,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,He’s not strong, so it’ll be easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:51.37,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,If you can use Fullbring, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:52.97,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:07.84,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:10.52,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Why’re you running away? You’re pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.91,0:08:13.30,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Fight him! Be a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:14.70,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:18.73,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t grasp the situation \NI’m in right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:21.46,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Facing him is out of the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:23.75,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:25.79,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,How did I become so tiny,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.79,0:08:28.73,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,and how did I get inside this toy box house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:30.09,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:34.03,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,That’s the power of \N“Dollhouse,” my Fullbring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.54,0:08:38.41,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Fullbring is the power of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.67,0:08:40.55,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Love?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:43.41,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s the ability to draw \Nout the maximum power
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:45.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,from something a person loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:50.52,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,A guy like Ginjo, who only \Nlikes his pendant, turns
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:53.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,that into a weapon to fight with.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.71,0:08:55.52,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,But I’m different!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.15,0:08:58.98,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,I have many things that I love,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:09:01.76,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,and I will find many more from here on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.76,0:09:04.70,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,I will spend my life collecting \Nthings that I love,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.70,0:09:08.20,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,and my wish is to die, smothered \Nby the things I love!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:13.25,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,“Dollhouse” is the ability for \Nthings that I’ve given permission to
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:17.26,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,move in and out of my favorite objects!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:24.66,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,I just gave you permission and invited \Nyou into my favorite box here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:26.61,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You’re enjoying this, aren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.32,0:09:29.60,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Explanation’s over!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:32.46,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Now, mind getting on with defeating this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.91,0:09:36.59,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t be chicken!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:38.04,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,You’ll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.04,0:09:42.03,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s set up so you can defeat him \Nif you’re able to use Fullbring!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.03,0:09:43.97,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Give it a try! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:45.74,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Are you nuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.74,0:09:49.97,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Is Fullbring supposed to be so easy \Nthat all I have to do is try?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.62,0:09:52.60,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I thought this was supposed to be training
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.60,0:09:54.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,to regain my Soul Reaper powers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.73,0:09:58.62,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have be able to use Fullbring?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.90,0:10:00.91,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,You sure yack a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:04.37,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep quiet and do as you’re told!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:07.39,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have to have an explanation \Nto put your life on the line?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.39,0:10:08.78,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,You suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:10.53,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize what you’re saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.53,0:10:12.38,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,You’re speaking like a dictator!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.95,0:10:17.63,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:19.60,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,You’re getting better at dodging!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:21.26,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.49,0:10:24.17,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t just watch, at least give me a hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:25.70,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,It’s crazy to expect me to use
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:28.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Fullbring without even a clue or hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:30.84,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,A hint?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.84,0:10:34.25,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,We were able to use Fullbring \Nfrom the moment we were born!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:37.01,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,How would I know any clues or hints!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.01,0:10:38.29,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.58,0:10:40.60,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.22,0:10:42.74,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn it! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:45.49,B2,MR. PORK,0000,0000,0000,,Hey…enough already, kid…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:46.41,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:50.42,B2,MR. PORK,0000,0000,0000,,Stop running away and start fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:53.59,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,It can talk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.77,0:10:55.47,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it talks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.47,0:10:57.22,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Inside “Mr. Pork” is a scary dude
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.22,0:10:59.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,that I abducted from this neighborhood!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.21,0:11:02.46,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You did what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.46,0:11:05.72,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, this thing’s name is Mr. Pork?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:07.43,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Where’s the love in that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.84,0:11:11.51,B2,MR. PORK,0000,0000,0000,,Stay still and let me kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:15.61,B2,MR. PORK,0000,0000,0000,,If I don’t beat you dead within 15 minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:17.77,B2,MR. PORK,0000,0000,0000,,this spell will become permanent
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.77,0:11:19.62,B2,MR. PORK,0000,0000,0000,,and I’ll be stuck inside this
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:22.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,goofy plushie for the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:25.20,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,And you threatened him with a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:27.51,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, “goofy”?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:29.40,B2,MR. PORK,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.72,0:11:32.92,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! That’s all the advice from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.11,0:11:35.07,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Call me when you’re done, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.69,0:11:37.24,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, wait, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.24,0:11:38.96,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:39.80,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, she closed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:40.65,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:42.37,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Let me out of here, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:44.60,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,I think I’ll have a snack!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:45.53,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,-Let me out, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:47.37,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,-Giriko, make me some tea!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:46.83,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,-Are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:50.60,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,I want a nice hot milk tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:53.81,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,The same kind they serve at \Nthe place in Henri Dubois!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.67,0:11:58.31,B2,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,Will he be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:11:59.48,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:02.67,B2,MR. PORK,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.67,0:12:04.28,B2,MR. PORK,0000,0000,0000,,Let me beat you dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:05.15,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn… {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:09.30,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She has no intention of letting me \Nout or giving any helpful advice… {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:11.16,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a nasty woman. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.98,0:12:18.75,B2,MR.PORK,0000,0000,0000,,I said stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:20.70,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Simply running won’t get me anywhere… {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.70,0:12:22.34,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I’ve got to think of something! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.39,0:12:26.64,B2,RIRUKA (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fullbring is the power of love! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:28.97,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The ability to draw out the maximum power {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:31.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}from something a person loves.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:36.39,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it didn’t seem like Ginjo \N“loves” that pendant… {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.76,0:12:39.57,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I had to say, it was more \Nlike an “attachment”… {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:43.71,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which means that for me to \Nbecome able to use Fullbring, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.71,0:12:46.03,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I’ll need an object like that. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:48.47,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isn’t there something? Something… {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.35,0:13:03.10,B2,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,If you’re so worried, \Nwhy don’t you help him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:08.81,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:10.07,B2,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, whatever…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.07,0:13:14.52,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,If he’s going to get killed so easily, \Nthen he wasn’t all that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.36,0:13:16.60,B2,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,But Riruka…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:17.96,B2,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:20.39,B2,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,That plushie has a timer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:21.78,B2,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,It’s going to be…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:23.66,B2,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,15 minutes soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:35.34,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for doing the shopping, Mr. Chad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.26,0:13:40.28,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,What’s that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:43.15,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,This is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:45.82,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,You’re already starting \Nhis Fullbring training?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:47.63,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean “already”?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:49.79,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,The sooner the better!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.79,0:13:52.77,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you criticizing my methods, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.22,0:13:59.91,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There’s got to be something… {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:05.10,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.10,0:14:06.03,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,Your Combat Pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:07.26,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute, Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:09.20,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:11.70,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,If you’re going to learn Fullbring,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:15.25,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,your Combat Pass is your only chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.59,0:14:17.81,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,We think alike!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.81,0:14:19.98,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.78,0:14:23.25,B2,VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,Time is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:28.66,B2,VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,As stipulated, because Fullbring \Nwas not detected within 15 minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,0:14:31.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,“Crazy Beast Mode” will be activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.18,0:14:34.49,B2,MR. PORK,0000,0000,0000,,Please...don’t!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:42.22,B2,MR. PORK,0000,0000,0000,,This is cruel…don’t…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:48.99,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,W-What’s happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:55.49,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:58.66,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the timer has been activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:25.46,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.22,0:15:28.84,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,You didn’t tell me he was \Ngoing to become that hideous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.35,0:15:31.49,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,What were you thinking, Giriko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:34.37,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,My, my…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:38.96,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one who asked my help in
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:41.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,training Mr. Ichigo, Miss Riruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.66,0:15:43.13,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:45.05,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,You didn’t have to make it so hideous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.05,0:15:47.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There must’ve been any \Nnumber of other ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.29,0:15:51.63,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I couldn’t think of any…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:53.19,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.19,0:15:54.08,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,Riruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:57.28,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,Let Ichigo out of this box right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:01.02,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.16,0:16:06.89,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Like the plushie, that box \Nhas a timer on it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:11.58,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,“If the organism inside \Ncan survive for 30 minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:14.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,then it can exit the box.”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:16.49,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of condition is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.27,0:16:21.18,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,You left the conditions up to me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:27.44,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Removing Mr. Ichigo from the box now \Nwould be a violation of the terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:31.57,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, the god of \Ntime will seek retribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.49,0:16:34.03,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,God of time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:38.75,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I believe this is the first \Ntime I told you about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:41.43,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,The timer is set such that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:47.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,in the event of a breach, \Nall objects being timed
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.42,0:16:52.07,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,will be burned away without \Na trace by the Flame of Time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:55.30,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,You’re bluffing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.98,0:16:58.35,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,You can believe me or not, that is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:03.03,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not a bluff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.61,0:17:05.92,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve seen it happen many times…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:19.72,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Convinced?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.29,0:17:23.91,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you understand, let me repeat myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:27.31,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,If, before another 15 minutes go by,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.61,0:17:32.38,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,either Mr. Ichigo or Mr. Pork \Nis removed from the box,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:35.70,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Ichigo, Mr. Pork and the box,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:39.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,all three will be consumed \Nby the Flame of Time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:47.62,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,That is my Fullbring, \N“Time Tells No Lies.”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:49.63,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,Deactivate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:53.76,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,That is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:57.27,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Once set, Time Tells No \NLies cannot be undone,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.27,0:18:02.34,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,even by myself, who controls its power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:05.23,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,A mistake in setting the terms…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.63,0:18:07.77,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,leads to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.03,0:18:11.11,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t ever take it lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.34,0:18:17.24,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Meddling with time is a frightening thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:21.16,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:24.61,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the next tea is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:28.12,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like another cup, Miss Riruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:33.59,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Ah…a wonderful aroma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.37,0:18:37.80,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,God dwells in exact time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.51,0:19:15.53,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do I do? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:20.91,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I’m to manifest this Fullbring \Nthing using my Combat Pass… {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:23.33,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How do I do it? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:26.36,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fullbring is… {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.15,0:19:33.34,B2,GINJO (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our ability is drawing out the \N“soul” in an object and {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.34,0:19:35.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}putting that object to use.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:39.50,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to draw out the \Nsoul of the Combat Pass. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:42.53,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How am I supposed to do that?! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.39,0:19:44.45,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How?! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.19,0:19:49.37,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,Your pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:55.94,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,When I first became able to \Nuse Brazo Derecho Del Gigante,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:19:59.42,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,what was in my heart was pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:02.72,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,The material that forms \Nthe basis for my Fullbring
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:04.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,is the skin on my two arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.98,0:20:05.88,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Skin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:11.06,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,My skin is on the dark side because \NI have Mestizo blood in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:14.84,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,My appearance! My big body!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.14,0:20:17.50,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,They’ve caused me lots of difficult times!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:21.20,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,But I never lost the pride I had in my skin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.89,0:20:24.37,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to be proud…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.65,0:20:26.37,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,because of my Abuelo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.21,0:20:31.18,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,My grandfather gave me \Nthe strength to be proud!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.77,0:20:37.47,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,Think back, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.94,0:20:39.83,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,Remember the time when you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.83,0:20:41.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,were proud of your Soul Reaper powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:46.79,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,The Combat Pass will respond to your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.34,0:20:48.57,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,Remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.57,0:20:49.60,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:57.06,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I was proud of my Soul Reaper powers? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.91,0:21:23.23,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There were… {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.62,0:21:29.39,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Too many times to count!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.46,0:23:23.64,B2,MR. PORK,0000,0000,0000,,If I lose this fight, I’ll be stuck \Nlike this for the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.64,0:23:25.25,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,It’s okay. You’ll turn back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.25,0:23:27.77,B2,MR. PORK,0000,0000,0000,,I swear that chick is an evil witch!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.77,0:23:30.30,B2,MR. PORK,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going to be stuck like this until
